text:
Thousands of children have been displaced by the floods in Brazil and want to go home. Today, you can make a difference for those in need and help them find safety. Donate now.

#HelpBrazil #BrazilFloodRelief
alt_text: Crowded indoor shelter with people on scattered mattresses after a flood in Brazil.
user_description: UNICEF works in over 190 countries and territories to protect children's rights. We won't stop, #ForEveryChild.

text:
»I just want to go home.« whispers João, 5, displaced by the floods in Brazil. His story is one of many, but today, you can make a difference for him. Help João and other children like him find safety. Donate now.

#HelpJoao #BrazilFloodRelief
alt_text: Young boy João sleeps on a mattress in a makeshift shelter after the flood in Brazil.
user_description: UNICEF works in over 190 countries and territories to protect children's rights. We won't stop, #ForEveryChild.
